721450f-a.title: Manhattan: Madison Avenue - 88th Street
721450f-a.text:
Madison Avenue at S.W. corner of 88th Street, the St. Lawence,
7-story apartment house.
It has subsequently been taken down, and the entire block from 87th
to 88th Street filled (1929) by a large 73 family apartment
building with stores.
About 1922.
0ift of E. M. Jenks.
